-- Four People Stabbed, Others Injured in Ibaraki Knife Attack, Kyodo Reports
-- B y   S t e v e n   M c P h e r s o n
-- 2010-12-17T00:54:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-17/four-people-stabbed-others-injured-in-ibaraki-knife-attack-kyodo-reports.html
Four people were stabbed in a knife
attack near a train station in Ibaraki prefecture, Japan, Kyodo
News reported. Several others were injured trying to escape the
attack, according to the report, which cited local fire
department officials.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven McPherson at 
 smcpherson@bloomberg.net  